originalText.text: Dr. Osher is a caring physician with an insightful and attentive approach to this patient. I feel very comfortable under her care. The staff is great, and my experience there has been satisfying overall. The new office space is perfect, and I scored a fine espresso on my last visit, to boot. She is well worth consideration for your general medical care.

originalText.text: Excellent first visit. Dr. Osher has a kind and caring approach and took the time to provide a complete overall picture of health which was very important to me. originalText.text: I have been going to Doctor Annette Osher for a few years now and always get outstanding service and support from Dr. Osher as well as her Assistant Vanessa. Dr. Osher is a very kind, highly skilled and attentive Doctor. She really listens to what is going on and recommends/takes all the right steps towards the health of her patients. Her assistant Vanessa is always on top of everything, very kind, skilled and professional. Best decision I have made to switch to Dr. Osher's practice.

originalText.text: I’m so happy that I found Dr. Osher. She is so attentive to patient care and was able to inform me on things I didn’t even know we’re going on with my body. It was the most thorough physical I’ve ever had. I am happy to be a patient at a practice where patient care is top priority genuinely.  It’s also worth mention the atmosphere of the office is so relaxing and inviting. Thank you for what you do Dr. Osher!
